e, NS 1987A may have\nenhanced cooling and/or a heavy-element envelope.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Apr 2020 17:22:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 May 2020 17:26:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-04"}
