 $\\mu$-Futaki invariant for general test configuration,\nand furthermore, it also produces an analogue of the equivariant first Chern\nclass of CM line bundle for family of polarized schemes, which is irrational\nand hence cannot be realized as a $\\mathbb{Q}$-line bundle in our general\n$\\mu$K-stability setup.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 09:57:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 15:46:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-25"}
