n from D.\nY. Kang et al. regarding $r$-matchings and improve a bound from G\\'orska and\nSkupie\\'n on the number of maximal matchings on trees. Remark that this\napproach is easily generalizable to graphs of bounded tree width or clique\nwidth (or any similar class of graphs where tree automata are meaningful).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 13:49:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Apr 2020 08:41:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 12:03:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-08"}
