y by analyzing the dominant terms in their effective\nHamiltonians.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 15:32:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 15:05:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-18"}
